      • login

        public static OAuthUser login(OAuthUser template,
                              javax.servlet.http.HttpSession session)
        Tries to log in the user in with all UserSessionManager. Stops at the first one that succeeds and returns the user which was the result of the login attempt. Will return null if no UserSessionManager could log the user in
        Parameters:
        template - a dummy user that holds enough information to uniquely identify her within a given UserSessionManager
        session - the request that initiated this login
        Returns:
        see description
